alwaysApply: true
---

Authoritative build spec: `docs/implementation-spec.md`.

MVP (Milestones 0–1): browser app at `http://127.0.0.1:8765`. No Electron until Milestone 3.

Always use LLMClient (`backend/services/llm_client.py`) for all AI calls.
Only `llm_client.py` may import the `anthropic` SDK — never in agent files.

Agents run sequentially. Never introduce parallel or concurrent agent execution.

Pipeline runs as a FastAPI BackgroundTask and publishes to ProgressBus.
All pipeline progress must reach the frontend via SSE — never client polling.

Use sync SQLAlchemy with `def` route handlers (threadpool). No async DB driver yet.
Bind uvicorn to `127.0.0.1` only.
